iChineseReader is the first online Chinese leveled reading platform for K-12 Chinese learners. This completely upgraded and updated version can serve your reading needs even better!

Features:

• Levelled reading section spanning 20 levels;
• Hundreds of titles by classroom teachers for classroom use;
• A comprehensive class management system empowering teachers to deliver differentiated reading assignments;
• Post-reading eQuizzes providing immediate feedbacks to assess comprehension;
• A new motivation game to inspire progressive self-reading at the reader’s own pace.

Please contact us to schedule a presentation for your school or a free trial today!

myDua - a pocket collection of prayers for all occasions. With the mobile app myDua you will always know how you should behave and what prayer to use in different situations. 

myDua app is optimized for all models of iPhone / iPad. This means that you will be able to fully enjoy all its beauty and usability.

Functions:

- Quick search by titles and content;
- Audio version of all prayers with ability to clean cache;
- Ability to add prayers to favourites;
- Amazing toolbar which allows to adjust screen brightness, font size and background color;
- Everyday push notification with ability to change time;
- Ability to share prayers with your friends using SMS, e-mail, social networks and messengers.

If you like the app, please leave your review in the App Store, and be sure to share the link with your friends! :)
- - - - -
Please notice that we can not reply to App Store reviews. If you have faced any issue, found a bug or have a great idea of how to make app better - feel fre to email us at support@mydua.me.

myQuran application is your universal assistant, which allows you to benefit from reading and listening to the Quran. myQuran will always be at your fingertips, wherever you are.

Features:

— Translation into 25 languages;
— Tafsir - interpretation of the Quran;
— Original Quran text with tajweed rules;
— Detailed information for each surah;
— Screen with Ajza;
— Easy to use and functional audio player;
— Ability to play each ayah separately (for 11 recitors);
— Interactive surah and ayah search; 
— Ability to add ayahs to favourites;
— Bookmarks;
— Custom font and font sizes;
— Quick access toolbar on the main screen;
— Ability to delete cached audio files;
— Customizable notifications;
— 3D touch support;

Please keep in mind, that you can share ayahs using e-mail, SMS, Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, Telegram, VK and other social networks. 

The application allows you to listen to Quran recitation with the voices of the best reciters in the world. Such as: Abdul Baset Abdus Samad; Abdul Rahman al-Sudais; Abdullah Awad al-Juhani; Abdullah Ibn Ali Basfar; Abu Bakr ash-Shatri; Ahmad bin Ali al-Ajmi; Emad al-Mansary; Hani ar-Rifai; Maher al-Muaiqly; Mahmood al-Rifai; Mahmoud Khalil al-Hussary; Mishari Rashid al-Afasy; Muhammad al-Luhaidan; Muhammad al-Minshawi; Nasser al-Qatami; Saad al-Ghamdi; Salah Abdul Rahman Bukhatir; Salah al-Budair; Salah al-Hashim; Saud al-Shuraim; Tawfeeq al-Sayegh; Yasser al-Dosari.

Please write your reviews and suggestions to support@myquran.me. We appreciate your opinion!

O ABC do Bita é um abecedário interativo em português que funciona como um brinquedo para crianças em início de alfabetização. Seus jogos educativos estimulam o raciocínio lógico, a coordenação motora e o desenvolvimento dos pequenos.

Toda criança vai adorar se divertir, interagir e aprender brincando com o um lindo aplicativo que fortalece o laço afetivo entre pais e filhos.
A cada letra, uma nova brincadeira. Faça o macaco balançar, o helicóptero voar e os milhos virarem pipoca. Divirta-se com a mais nova aventura do Bita e sua trupe.

- Auxilia na alfabetização;
- Estimula a criatividade, raciocínio lógico e a coordenação    motora da criança;
- Possuí narração profissional em português;
- Navegação fácil e intuitiva;
- Interação em cada letra;
- Jogos educativos para um aprendizado divertido;
- Animações interativas;
- Design inovador;
- Trilha sonora original e cativante.

